The Jumeirah Lakes Towers is a large development in Dubai, United Arab Emirates which consists of 80 towers being constructed along the edges of three artificial lakes as well as the JLT Embankment of eight towers facing Jumeirah Islands. V3 Tower JLT, Superb stay !!
Aug 2023 ‚Ä¢ Family
This is for V3 tower at JLT.

Amazing apartment! Absolutely huge and being on top floor with great views. All rooms are big and adequate for family stay. Location is great with shops nearby. There is a 24x7 mini supermarket located in the building which is so convenient. Kitchen has all the facilities and utensils required. Lounge is great with a very big size TV to relax and unwind. Beds are comfortable. Bedrooms are brilliant size with plenty of storage / walk in space. Access to a great swimming pool area (rooftop), gymnasium and also sauna on the floor above¬† Underground parking space available should you hire a car as well.

Pillows could have been cleaned / changed as they were still smelling of previous occupants.
Air conditioning in some rooms difficult to turn on / off and adjust.
Overall, brilliant stay and highly recommended!
